The,Australian,Synchrotron,is,Australia,s,largest,national,research,facility,The,synchrotron,produces,extremely,bright,x,rays,and,infrared,light,that,can,be,used,to,study,a,diverse,range,of,materials,and,processes,in,great,detail,Australian,Synchrotron,provides,several,SOAP,based,APIs,such,as,the,MyTARDIS,interface,and,the,VBL,Storage,Gateway,to,view,manage,and,transfer,experimental,data,in,a,secure,manner,Further,information,on,these,services,requires,user,log,in,or,an,email,to,the,provider